WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.435
The bedrock of all effective leadership is self-awareness. Before you

00:00:03.435 --> 00:00:06.870
can lead a global matrix organization, you must be intimately

00:00:06.870 --> 00:00:10.305
aware of your own cognitive and emotional architecture. Your internal

00:00:10.305 --> 00:00:13.740
values dictate your problem perception, which in turn drives your

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:17.175
external actions.
